    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（愛には体調が戻るまで、仕事も学校も休んでもらう）\n（ことにしたが……寮に一人きりにするのは、心配だな）",
      "startTime": 4.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（連絡を入れて、少し様子を見に行ってみるか……）",
      "startTime": 9.8112701733,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9587.1195953,
          "startTime": 19.3983897686
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（結局寮につくまで、メッセの返信はなかったが……）\n（……ん？）",
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがいる……！？\n夢じゃない、よね……えっと、お、お疲れ様です……",
      "startTime": 22.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日は大変ご迷惑をおかけしました……\nそのうえ病院にまで連れて行ってくれて……",
      "startTime": 30.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、お礼が先？　それともお詫び？\nまず何から言えば……",
      "startTime": 36.9361895469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "まずは落ち着いてくれ。それと気にしないでくれ\nそれより具合はどうだ？",
      "startTime": 43.1246095181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、ただの風邪と過労でしたし、昨日より元気です！\n今、ちょうど水を飲みに行こうと思って……",
      "startTime": 51.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、良かった。少しだけ安心したよ\nところで愛、昼食は食べたのか？",
      "startTime": 58.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……まだです。食欲がなくて……\n何か食べて薬を飲まないと",
      "startTime": 66.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ昼食は俺が用意するよ",
      "startTime": 69.5778228918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "用意？　もしかして作るんですか……？\n{user}さんの手料理……",
      "startTime": 77.3333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "簡単なものしか作れないから、期待はしないでくれ\n……今日は寮に誰もいないから、心細いんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 85.2333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、全部私のせいですから\n私が急にダウンしちゃったせいで",
      "startTime": 92.9000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "私がやるはずだった仕事の代打に行ってもらってるので\nみんなに申し訳ないです",
      "startTime": 100.3666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "困った時は、お互いに助け合えばいいんだ\nそれじゃあ、少し待っててくれ",
      "startTime": 107.0333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます\n楽しみに待ってますね",
      "startTime": 111.4666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの作ってくれた親子うどん\nとっても美味しかったです、ごちそうさまでした！",
      "startTime": 119.0333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "卵もうどんもとろっとろで……最高です！\n元気になったら自分でも作ってみようと思います！",
      "startTime": 127.9333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "愛には、ラーメンの方が良かったんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 131.6849432388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "もう、冗談ばっかり！　私だって\n一年中ラーメンばっかり食べてる訳じゃありませんよ",
      "startTime": 138.3666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はは、ごめん。残さず食べてくれて、安心したよ",
      "startTime": 142.1924033879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "お腹も一杯になって……少し、落ち着きました\n{user}さん、ありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 152.0333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "私が話せるようになるまで、待っててくれたんですよね\n昨日話せなかったこと……今、聞いてもらえますか？",
      "startTime": 160.4206486399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、聞かせてくれ。自分のペースでいいから",
      "startTime": 165.9445801814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "はい……東京シーサイドとのタイアップの後\n私達がライブバトルをしたの、覚えてますか？",
      "startTime": 175.9000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルには勝ちましたけど……\nでも、ギリギリでした",
      "startTime": 183.2666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "その時、思っちゃったんです\n私達はこんなに頑張って、実力だってついて",
      "startTime": 189.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "魅せるパフォーマンスだって\n出来てるつもりだったのに……",
      "startTime": 195.7666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、自分で思ってるより\n実力も頑張りも、足りてなかったのかなって……",
      "startTime": 202.4666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか……愛は努力を重ね、少しずつだが自信も）\n（ついてきていた。そんな中での、あの結果だったから）",
      "startTime": 212.2000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_09_02-ai020.m4a",
